In this edition of ReTrender The Zeitans, Jack and Miles discuss the Sunset Park shooting, the new season of Stranger Things, Gilbert Gottfried passing away, Brittney Griner STILL being detained in Russia, the new social media app 'BeReal', and the new film 'Father Stu'!
